rows.label: qst702702_msg0001
rows.name:
So this is the monster
blocking the bridge.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0002
rows.name: Sorry, but that's not your place!

rows.label: qst702702_msg0101
rows.name:
I see. It's blocking
the bridge perfectly.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0102
rows.name: What an inconsiderate monster.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0103
rows.name:
To hear that from you... I almost
sympathize with the monster.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0104
rows.name: Hey, what's that supposed to mean?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0105
rows.name:
He's saying he's looking
forward to it, in his own way.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0106
rows.name: Well then... are you two ready?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0201
rows.name:
I see. It's blocking
the bridge perfectly.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0202
rows.name: What an inconsiderate monster.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0203
rows.name:
To hear that from you... I almost
sympathize with the monster.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0204
rows.name: Hey, what's that supposed to mean?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0205
rows.name:
...Laura-sama, do you think
those two will be alright?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0206
rows.name: Hmm...

rows.label: qst702702_msg0207
rows.name:
It's surprisingly difficult to
say what you really think.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0208
rows.name:
In the sense that they can do that,
maybe they're not so incompatible?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0209
rows.name: Who, with this guy?

rows.label: qst702702_msg0210
rows.name:
I'll return those words to you
exactly as you said them.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0211
rows.name: What a jerk!

rows.label: qst702702_msg0212
rows.name:
Ah, this harmonious feeling is
nice. Travelers stick together,
and the world is full of kindness.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0213
rows.name: ...It seems they want to join us.

rows.label: qst702702_msg0214
rows.name:
In that case, let's start
the welcoming party.
